Sweep trace: <filename>  (N operations, M total configs)

--- Operation: ttnn.experimental.all_gather_async ---
  Model configs: 28 | Sweep configs: 26
  Exact matches: 24/26
  Close matches: 1/26 (>=80% similarity)
  Unmatched sweep configs: 1
  Unmatched model configs: 3

  Config ID mapping (sweep -> model):
    Exact matches:
      sweep config_id 1  -> model config_id 212
      sweep config_id 3  -> model config_id 12
